----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Requirements
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Compulsory:

- a working C++ compiler
- autoconf 2.52+
- expat
- sablotron

Optional:

- zlib (for gzip/deflate support in mod_http)



----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

It follows the standard GNU guidelines, so read the INSTALL file for the
generic install instructions.

After you've compiled and installed prometeo, you can point your web browser
to http://localhost:8081 to access the configuration panel (or you can
manually edit the config file, prometeo.xml, which by default sits in
/usr/local/prometeo/etc).

Have fun. :)

